ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisEnactment of the NON-SIGNATORY YUKON FIRST NATIONS REMISSION ORDER which remits the Goods and Services Tax (GST) paid by certain Yukon First Nations (and their members) who have not entered into a Final Agreement, on purchases made between February 15, 1998 to March 31, 2002.
